author: The Slow Mo Guys
description:
Gav travels to Missouri to see what happens when the broadcast of a radio station takes a diversion through a hot dog. Don't try this at home with YOUR radio tower!
With Jeff Geerling! - @GeerlingEngineering  @JeffGeerling 
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/theslowmoguys
Tik Tok - https://www.tiktok.com/@theslowmoguys
Sound design painstakingly done by Daniel Fabelo 
Filmed with the Phantom TMX7510
title: Hot Dog vs 7000 W Radio Tower at 200,000 FPS - The Slow Mo Guys
